			<div class="content" id="post-content-2467899">
									

<p>Part 5 of a series.</p>
<p>Thanks to my teammates <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1458695664" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;">A Random Day</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1814684&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1458695664" alt="GreenWolf" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1814684)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;">GreenWolf</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2038009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1458695664" alt="TyGently" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2038009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;">TyGently</a></span> for brainstorming, strategy, feedback and support. Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2156983&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1458695664" alt="psul" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2156983)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;">psul</a></span> for feedback in the forums.</p>
<p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dmatix" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1366080); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1366080&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1458695664" alt="Dmatix" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1366080)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dmatix" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1366080); return false;">Dmatix</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/marqfja87" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1895233); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1895233&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1458695664" alt="MarqFJA87" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1895233)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/marqfja87" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1895233); return false;">MarqFJA87</a></span> for translation help.</p>
<p>Other entries:<br />
1. <a href="/avatara">Avatara</a>, by A Random Day<br />
2. <a href="/grant-request-for-investigating-the-potential-application-of">GRANT REQUEST FOR INVESTIGATING THE APPLICATION OF CERTAIN RESEARCH ASSETS IN OVERCOMING INHERENT LIMITATIONS OF THE HUMAN BODY</a> by GreenWolf<br />
3. <a href="/scp-2970">SCP-2970</a>, Holy Misplacement, by TyGently<br />
4. <a href="/operation-azure-peregrine">Operation AZURE PEREGRINE</a>, by sirpudding<br />
5. The Lord of Endowments, by sirpudding.<br />
6. <a href="/samsara">Samsara</a> by A Random Day and TyGently</p>
<p>This is my first GOI format article.</p>
<p>Commentary now available on <a href="/sirpudding-s-author-page">Sirpudding's Author Page</a>.</p>

