<li>He had the rat-wizard from the PL experimental line, which let him use some sympathetic magic to let him know that they were being attacked by something made of the same stuff, he had some clues from the reading they did eariler that warned them trouble was coming, and he was able to clairvoyantly observe the attack (including the Samsara troopers' rapid healing from wounds) as it progressed.</li>
<li>A Random Day can correct me if I am wrong but: They retained a large amount of training and knowledge from their previous identities, just not anything like clear personal memories and self-identity, as well as having received training since then. Nanku reads Arabic.</li>
<li>Yes and also &quot;The Witch, The Wizard and the Man of Steel&quot;, draft thread (which apparently is even slower than the fora here): <a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/forum/t-1495757/the-witch-the-wizard-and-the-man-of-steel-draft">http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/forum/t-1495757/the-witch-the-wizard-and-the-man-of-steel-draft</a>.</li>
