			<div class="content" id="post-content-2468897">
									

<blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>Prometheus Labs as &quot;Plunderers&quot; is quite nice, also.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Yeah I needed a SH/WL nickname for them, and as far as I can tell there wasn't any prior art that established one, although I am actually quite split between &quot;Plunderers&quot; and &quot;Pilferers&quot;. If anybody has a strong preference, please let me know!</p>
</blockquote>
<p>I'd go with &quot;Pilferers&quot;, myself. &quot;Plunder&quot; has the connotation of being stolen with violence, whereas Prometheus was a sneaky bugger (by necessity, violence against the gods tends to attract unwanted lightning).</p>

